{
  "stem": "9963.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The funny thing is, you know I laugh now about this, but there's such a tremendous thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When we came over there with the other camp, and we had to be the mechanics that are really professional people, they give us a shovel with a pick, you know, to go to dig over there the places, you know, to make a road.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They need professional people to that-- to make roads.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they give us a shovel with a pick, you know, to dig it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was after Buchenwald-- Holzminden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By trucks.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put us on a truck to get there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Buchenwald I was about two months, or maybe about 10 weeks or something like this I was in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to Holzminden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germany.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was, I said, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Over there we had to build roads.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the thing is that there were the big generals sitting, you know, and interviewing everybody, you know, what are mechanics and things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you had to be a really professional, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they come over there they give you a shovel with a pick axe, you know, to make roads.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We worked over there for several weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later, this-- right away, they get us to stop the work, put us in another camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the other camp when we came was Drutte.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we came over there and that camp was packed already to move, because the Allied soldiers were close.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't want to get the people who were there, so we stayed over there for a few days.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And again, put us on a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The train-- that train was very, very long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was at least-- not to exaggerate-- but five, six, locomotives to pull that train.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
